{"tid":1917412,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[支持Rthk] 台灣故事：會客菜","createTime":"2020-03-09T13:03:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-12T14:47:25.000Z","uid":41818,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b27718052be97fcc9b6150e90fa2363ebb527e11","tid":1917412,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T13:03:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/mCLp0pjof0A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FmCLp0pjof0A&d=80SwoNSEtZKcYq6iNhm%2FMwpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=d2ba69fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/mCLp0pjof0A</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在台灣大大小小的監獄附近，都總會找到一兩間不甚起眼的食檔；既無大魚大肉，亦不是甚麼撚手菜色，普普通通的小菜，賣的是家常味道，監獄裡面稱之為會客菜。會客菜給囚犯重拾少少家的滋味，在不經意間救贖了獄中痛悔心靈，熱騰騰的香味將罪人渡向新生。<br />\n<br />\n#一碗滷肉飯令人改過自新,#江湖大佬都幫襯的食檔,#監獄食物禁忌,#香腸雞鴨不可一齊點,#人生有take two"},{"pid":"7bf8a4bb6a36a9b368155a22dff95703e50b585c","tid":1917412,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T13:37:10.000Z","msg":"睇大佛普拉斯先知咩係會客菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1697d7756e7b175cef3f647423cdf56d31d2e36c","tid":1917412,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7bf8a4bb6a36a9b368155a22dff95703e50b585c","tid":1917412,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T13:37:10.000Z","msg":"睇大佛普拉斯先知咩係會客菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T13:38:21.000Z","msg":"未睇過，原來呢套戲有提及過呢樣嘢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80729f206638dc6dc1151a89742d6b5f0f71f115","tid":1917412,"uid":42848,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1697d7756e7b175cef3f647423cdf56d31d2e36c","tid":1917412,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7bf8a4bb6a36a9b368155a22dff95703e50b585c","tid":1917412,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T13:37:10.000Z","msg":"睇大佛普拉斯先知咩係會客菜<img src=